Name: Mazeing
About the game: 3D labyrinth game During the game you will have to solve minigames to finish the level. The size of the labyrinth is costomizable. For completeing a level you get coins that you can spend in the in-game shop for upgrades. You get a basic tutorial at the start and if you want there are other more advanced tutorials. If you like a map - by knowing it's code - you can replay it. What are you waiting for? Get it now! [labyrinth ] [3D] [minigames] [Dynamites]
